      </p>
     </div>
     <div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA05d025n1-ptr" id="PJA05d025n1">1</a>
      <p>Tudors <span class="choice reg" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover_choice ] header=[]  body=[ In letterpress edition: 'two' ]"><a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-01-03-02-0016-0203#DJA03Q1023" class="quote">first</a> and <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-01-03-02-0016-0203#DJA03Q1024" class="quote">second</a></span> letters were answered by <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ John Adams (17351826) ]">JA</abbr> on 26 Sept. (<span class="ref-st" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ &lt;i&gt;Diary and Autobiography of John Adams&lt;/i&gt;, ed. L. H. Butterfield and others, Cambridge, 1961; 4 vols. ]">JA, <span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">Diary and Autobiography</span></span>, 3:437441; see also Tudor to <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ John Adams (17351826) ]">JA</abbr>, 23 Sept., <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-06-05-02-0019&amp;expandNote=PJA05d021n6#PJA05d021n6" class="document">note 6</a>, above).</p>
     </div>
     <div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA05d025n2-ptr" id="PJA05d025n2">2</a>
      <p>See <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ John Adams (17351826) ]">JA</abbr> to James Warren, 25 Sept., <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-06-05-02-0020&amp;expandNote=PJA05d022n1#PJA05d022n1" class="document">note 1</a> (above).</p>
     </div>
     <div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA05d025n3-ptr" id="PJA05d025n3">3</a>
      <p>The resolution of the General Court stipulated that the drafted militiamen were to serve until recalled by the legislature or either branch of it (Records of the States, Microfilm, Mass. 1.1a, Reel No. 12, Unit 2, p. 546).</p>
